  "html": "<div class=\"mb-6\"> <h3 class=\"h3 mb-6\">設計流程 Process</h3> <img src=\"https://github.com/himihuang/portfolio/blob/main/src/assets/img/process_car.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" class=\"w-full\" /> </div> <div> <div class=\"mb-6\"> <h3 class=\"h3 mb-6\">設計 Design</h3> <p>設計的部分，從汽車所呈現的速度感去發想，利用一些線條和斜角圖形去呈現汽車的速度感；顏色的部分用黑色搭配黃色，黑色帶有汽車的陽剛味，利用黃色點綴，讓陽剛味的網站帶有一點活潑感。</p> </div> <div class=\"mb-6\"> <h3 class=\"h3 mb-6\">資訊架構</h3> <img src=\"https://github.com/himihuang/portfolio/blob/main/src/assets/img/car_frame.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" class=\"w-full\"> </div> <div class=\"\"> <h3 class=\"h3 mb-6\">頁面介紹</h3> <div class=\"pb-6\"> <h4 class=\"h4 mb-6\">首頁</h4> <img src=\"https://github.com/himihuang/portfolio/blob/main/src/assets/img/car_img_1.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" class=\"w-full pb-4\"> </div> <div class=\"pb-6\"> <h4 class=\"h4 mb-6\">其他頁面</h4> <img src=\"https://github.com/himihuang/portfolio/blob/main/src/assets/img/car_img_2.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" class=\"w-full pb-4\"> <img src=\"https://github.com/himihuang/portfolio/blob/main/src/assets/img/car_img_3.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" class=\"w-full pb-4\"> <img src=\"https://github.com/himihuang/portfolio/blob/main/src/assets/img/car_img_4.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" class=\"w-full pb-4\"> <img src=\"https://github.com/himihuang/portfolio/blob/main/src/assets/img/car_img_5.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" class=\"w-full pb-4\"> <img src=\"https://github.com/himihuang/portfolio/blob/main/src/assets/img/car_img_6.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" class=\"w-full pb-4\"> <img src=\"https://github.com/himihuang/portfolio/blob/main/src/assets/img/car_img_7.png?raw=true\" alt=\"\" class=\"w-full pb-4\"> </div> </div> </div>"
